# Baked into every production build (`npm run build`) — however it's deployed (runner or manual copy).
# This is the TEST FactoryControl gateway that hosts the SCC `api` doPost.
# For a PROD build, the deploy.yml workflow sets VITE_SCC_API_BASE as a job env var, which
# takes precedence over this file (Vite: real env > .env files).
VITE_SCC_API_BASE=https://james-jef-tst.oshkoshglobal.com/system/webdev/FactoryControl/api
